        <item>
            <title>PS5 新专利：重返旧时剧情，玩家透过触发点回带游戏重要时刻</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/14/content-streaming-with-gameplay-launch/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=content-streaming-with-gameplay-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/14/content-streaming-with-gameplay-launch/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 11:26:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Content Streaming With Gameplay Launch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[playstation]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[专利]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1204272</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>现时玩家若然想回顾单人游戏的某个时刻，通常需要花费数小时才能回到那个点。最近有消息指，Sony 正为 PlayStation 申请一项名为「Content Streaming With Gameplay Launch」的新专利，让玩家可透过「触发点」重温特定时刻和剪切场景。</p><p>虽然尚未清楚新专利如何运作，但 Sony 称每个触发点都可与一组游戏数据相连，而游戏数据则与游戏场景相连。原理与 DVD 的章节相似，一旦玩家解锁触发点，装置便会根据所选触发点的已识别游戏资料集启动游戏，因此解锁触发点便可于事后重新连接至特定游戏场景。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-13-08.50.23.png"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1204294" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-13-08.50.23-694x467.png" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-13-08.50.23-694x467.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-13-08.50.23-1280x861.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-13-08.50.23-768x517.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-13-08.50.23.png 1430w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>外媒估计，新专利有可能在《Marvel&#8217;s Wolverine》及第三方游戏《Final Fantasy VII Rebirth》等地方出现，但不清楚会否应用至《Marvel&#8217;s Spider-Man 2》等现有游戏中。</p><p>Sony 多年来成功申请过不少专利，但有部分尚未有应用至游戏中，当中包括以日用品取替 PS5 控制器。因此即使 Sony 成功申请新专利，未来也不一定会在的游戏中看到「Content Streaming With Gameplay Launch」的身影。</p><p>图片来源：PlayStation</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/playstation-patent-single-player-game-feature-sony-ps5/">ComicBook.com</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

